---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 13, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service · Viva Wellness Co."
  description="The terms that govern your use of vivawellnessco.com, including membership policies, medical disclaimers, and how clinical care is established."
>

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container legal-hero__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">· Terms</span>
      <h1 class="legal-hero__title">
        How this <span class="italic-display">works.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lead">
        The terms that govern your use of this website and our memberships.
        Plain language, short paragraphs, no surprises.
      </p>
      <p class="legal-hero__updated">Last updated · {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="container legal-body__inner">

      <div class="legal-callout">
        <strong>The short version.</strong>
        This website is informational. Visiting it does not create a patient
        relationship. To start care, you book a telehealth visit and complete
        intake. Memberships have a twelve-week minimum and can be cancelled
        any time after.
      </div>

      <h2 class="legal-h">By using this site, you agree</h2>
      <p>
        You are eighteen years or older. You are using this website for
        personal, non-commercial purposes. You will not attempt to disrupt the
        site, scrape it at scale, or use it in any way that violates law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">This website is not medical advice</h2>
      <p>
        Everything on this site, including the protocol-match quiz, the eBook,
        and the blog, is educational. Reading or downloading any of it does
        <strong>not</strong> establish a doctor-patient or
        provider-patient relationship. It is not a substitute for individual
        clinical evaluation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Clinical care begins when you book a telehealth visit, complete intake,
        and the provider accepts you as a patient. From that point forward, all
        clinical communication happens in our patient portal (Charm Health),
        not on this website or in generic email.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Memberships</h2>
      <p>
        Membership tiers, what they include, and our cancellation policy are
        listed in detail on the <a href="/services">programs</a> page. The key
        points:
      </p>
      <ul class="legal-list">
        <li>All memberships require a twelve-week minimum. This gives the protocol enough runway to produce measurable results.</li>
        <li>After the initial twelve weeks, you can cancel any time with no penalty.</li>
        <li>Memberships renew automatically every thirty days. You can update or remove your card on file at any point.</li>
        <li>Medication, supplies, and shipments continue while your membership is active.</li>
        <li>We accept FSA and HSA. Insurance is not applied to membership fees but may apply to labs and non-compounded medications.</li>
        <li>Every protocol requires provider review and approval. We do not dispense based on a checkbox.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Provider licensure and service area</h2>
      <p>
        Viva Wellness Co. is a one-hundred-percent telehealth practice operated
        by licensed providers. We currently see patients in Texas, Colorado,
        and Florida. If you are physically located in a state where our
        providers are not licensed at the time of a visit, that visit cannot
        proceed.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Medication sourcing</h2>
      <p>
        Compounded medications dispensed for our patients come from
        FDA-regulated 503A compounding pharmacies that perform third-party
        testing for potency and sterility. We do not work with grey-market
        peptide vendors. If a medication is not appropriate for you clinically,
        the provider will not prescribe it, regardless of the membership tier.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        All content on this site, including text, images, the eBook, and the
        Viva Wellness Co. wordmark, is our property or licensed to us. Personal
        reading and reasonable sharing is encouraged. Republishing without
        attribution or commercial use without written permission is not.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Disclaimers and limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        This website is provided as-is. While we keep it accurate, we make no
        warranty that it is error-free or always available. To the extent
        permitted by law, our liability for any issue arising from your use of
        this website is limited to the amount you paid to access it, which for
        this website is zero. Clinical care under an active membership is
        separately governed by the documents you sign at intake.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms. When we do, we will revise the date at the
        top. Continued use of the site after an update means you accept the
        revised terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Texas. Any dispute
        that cannot be resolved by ordinary conversation will be handled in the
        courts of Travis County, Texas.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Questions</h2>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:info@vivawellnessco.com">info@vivawellnessco.com</a>
        or call <a href="tel:+17372107283">(737) 210-7283</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="legal-foot">
        Viva Wellness Co. · 5900 Balcones Dr #19640, Austin, TX 78731
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 11vw, 9rem) 0 clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .legal-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(800px 500px at 75% 0%, rgba(201, 120, 58, 0.14), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .legal-hero__inner { position: relative; max-width: 70ch; }
  .legal-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6.5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-hero__title .italic-display { color: var(--bronze-bright); }
  .legal-hero__updated {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mute);
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    padding-top: 1.2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .legal-body { padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem); }
  .legal-body__inner { max-width: 70ch; margin: 0 auto; }

  .legal-callout {
    background: var(--ink-2);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--bronze);
    padding: 1.6rem 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 234, 0.9);
  }
  .legal-callout strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bronze);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .legal-h {
    font-family: var(--font-display-italic);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.6vw, 1.9rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 2.8rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .legal-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 234, 0.85);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .legal-body a {
    color: var(--bronze);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 120, 58, 0.4);
    transition: color 200ms var(--ease), border-color 200ms var(--ease);
  }
  .legal-body a:hover {
    color: var(--bronze-bright);
    border-color: var(--bronze-bright);
  }
  .legal-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-list li {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 234, 0.85);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .legal-list li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .legal-list strong { color: var(--paper); }

  .legal-foot {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--mute);
  }
</style>
